\subsection{Spatial Inputs}{

Input data can be provided as:
\itemize{
\item An \code{sf} object — geometry column is used for coordinates automatically.
\item A \code{data.frame} with columns \code{x} and \code{y} (or \code{lon} and \code{lat}).
